page.title: 07Woodsetts Village
page.content: The{Woodsetts church}was built in {1847.}In Woodsetts there is a playing field which has a slide, swings,a roundabout and climbing frame.There is a football pitch and a cricket pitch.There is a new football pitch being made.The{playing field}is called the rec and is surrounded by houses.On the rec there is a stream which runs round the edge.In the centre of the rec there is a pavilion.It is used for parties, dancing and playgroups.We have several{clubs}in the village which are the golf club and a football club a cricket club cubs, scouts, brownies and guides .There is a meeting point where ladies go to talk.There is a{sunday school}in the village where people sing songs and learn about God.It starts at 10:30 a.m and finishes about 11:40 a.m.
